text: Marasany () is a rural locality (a village) in Polozovoskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 87 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 13 km north from Polozovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Marasany
